910
01:16:45,502 --> 01:16:47,250
What do you want?

911
01:16:47,639 --> 01:16:49,773
Please just tell
me what you want!

912
01:16:49,774 --> 01:16:51,175
We want you! (SHRIEKS)

913
01:16:51,176 --> 01:16:52,958
(SCREAMING)

914
01:16:55,144 --> 01:16:58,393
[SALLY]: Daddy!
Daddy, please!

915
01:17:01,885 --> 01:17:03,393
Daddy!

916
01:17:05,625 --> 01:17:07,132
[ALEX]: Sally?

917
01:17:07,390 --> 01:17:09,167
- Daddy!
- Sally?

918
01:17:11,329 --> 01:17:12,427
Daddy!

919
01:17:12,428 --> 01:17:15,074
(CREATURES SNARLING)

920
01:17:16,801 --> 01:17:19,203
Daddy, they're in here!

921
01:17:19,204 --> 01:17:21,282
Open the door!
Sally!

922
01:17:25,075 --> 01:17:26,788
(SCREAMS)

923
01:17:34,885 --> 01:17:36,184
Charles.

924
01:17:36,185 --> 01:17:37,795
[KIM]: What's going
on in there?

925
01:17:41,792 --> 01:17:43,539
- (SCREECHING)
- (SCREAMING)

926
01:17:43,727 --> 01:17:46,941
No! Get off of me!
Stop it!

927
01:17:50,467 --> 01:17:51,883
(SCREAMING)

928
01:17:53,937 --> 01:17:56,355
(GASPING)

929
01:18:11,655 --> 01:18:13,436
(SHRIEKING)

930
01:18:17,662 --> 01:18:19,928
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

931
01:18:19,929 --> 01:18:21,346
[KIM]: Sally!

932
01:18:21,964 --> 01:18:23,747
(ALL MURMURING)

933
01:18:26,236 --> 01:18:27,470
Sally. Sally.

934
01:18:27,471 --> 01:18:30,185
Look at me.
Sally, look at me. Look at me.

935
01:18:30,574 --> 01:18:33,821
Picture,
I took a picture.

936
01:18:38,081 --> 01:18:40,295
(SOBBING)

937
01:18:43,286 --> 01:18:44,721
I think we better
call it a night.

938
01:18:44,722 --> 01:18:46,639
I think we should.

939
01:18:54,732 --> 01:18:56,706
It's okay.
It's okay.

940
01:19:26,263 --> 01:19:28,409
Alex, can I talk to you?

941
01:19:33,670 --> 01:19:36,111
I feel like I have
no idea what to do.

942
01:19:45,849 --> 01:19:47,926
I love my daughter, Kim,

943
01:19:51,621 --> 01:19:53,368
and I love you.

944
01:19:56,460 --> 01:19:58,275
I love you, too.

945
01:19:59,796 --> 01:20:01,713
We should go, right?

946
01:20:03,032 --> 01:20:05,508
- I'll get Sally ready.
- I'll get the car.

947
01:20:31,694 --> 01:20:33,596
- Will you put this in the car?
- Yeah.

948
01:20:33,597 --> 01:20:36,015
(THUNDER RUMBLING)

949
01:20:50,180 --> 01:20:52,461
(ENGINE STARTING)

950
01:21:03,228 --> 01:21:04,701
[SALLY]: Kim?

951
01:21:06,230 --> 01:21:07,646
Hi.

952
01:21:09,234 --> 01:21:10,850
Where are we going?

953
01:21:11,869 --> 01:21:13,902
We're gonna go
to a hotel downtown.

954
01:21:13,903 --> 01:21:15,820
We're gonna get you
out of here.

955
01:21:47,138 --> 01:21:49,178
(GRUNTING)

956
01:22:30,214 --> 01:22:31,754
Alex?

957
01:23:05,047 --> 01:23:06,556
Alex?

958
01:23:10,753 --> 01:23:12,262
Alex?

959
01:23:30,140 --> 01:23:31,887
It's okay, it's okay.

960
01:23:47,523 --> 01:23:48,941
(GASPS)

961
01:23:50,760 --> 01:23:52,227
(GROANS IN PAIN)

962
01:23:52,228 --> 01:23:54,874
