969
01:24:23,960 --> 01:24:25,967
Sally!

970
01:24:26,496 --> 01:24:28,938
Child's teeth!

971
01:24:32,703 --> 01:24:34,211
Kim?

972
01:24:45,082 --> 01:24:46,499
Kim?

973
01:24:48,418 --> 01:24:50,753
