974
01:24:50,754 --> 01:24:52,296
Kim?

975
01:24:53,355 --> 01:24:54,830
Daddy?

976
01:25:06,902 --> 01:25:09,981
(CREATURES WHISPERING)

977
01:25:10,740 --> 01:25:12,486
Kim?

978
01:25:20,751 --> 01:25:22,258
Kim?

979
01:25:46,176 --> 01:25:47,820
(CREATURES WHISPER)
(GASPS)

980
01:25:54,718 --> 01:25:55,784
(SCREAMS)

981
01:25:55,785 --> 01:25:57,260
Kim!

982
01:25:57,754 --> 01:26:00,105
Kim! Please.

983
01:26:02,223 --> 01:26:03,458
Kim.

984
01:26:03,459 --> 01:26:05,261
Wake up, please!
(CREATURES CHATTERING)

985
01:26:05,262 --> 01:26:08,647
[CREATURES CHANTING]:
Wake up, Kim. Wake up, Kim.

986
01:26:08,931 --> 01:26:11,666
Wake up Kim.
Wake up Kim.

987
01:26:11,667 --> 01:26:13,516
Wake up, Kim.

988
01:26:15,838 --> 01:26:17,255
