01:27:55,272 --> 01:27:56,744
Sally?

1007
01:28:01,343 --> 01:28:02,760
Ah.

1008
01:28:09,818 --> 01:28:10,919
Ah!

1009
01:28:10,920 --> 01:28:13,168
Sally? Sally!

1010
01:28:14,356 --> 01:28:16,207
[SALLY]: Kim!

1011
01:28:25,868 --> 01:28:27,786
[SALLY]: Let go of me!

1012
01:28:28,371 --> 01:28:30,038
