01:29:48,985 --> 01:29:50,117
Get away from me!

1032
01:29:50,118 --> 01:29:51,536
Get off of me!

1033
01:29:51,720 --> 01:29:53,638
(SCREECHING)

1034
01:29:55,657 --> 01:29:57,904
(SHRIEKING)

1035
01:29:58,328 --> 01:30:00,177
(GRUNTING)

1036
01:30:01,463 --> 01:30:03,663
When I cut this rope, Sally,
you run!

1037
01:30:03,664 --> 01:30:04,867
Please!

1038
01:30:04,868 --> 01:30:06,368
You run!
You got that?

1039
01:30:06,369 --> 01:30:08,446
No, what about you?

1040
01:30:09,305 --> 01:30:10,540
No! Please!

1041
01:30:10,541 --> 01:30:12,008
[KIM]: Be strong.

1042
01:30:12,009 --> 01:30:14,288
(GRUNTING)

1043
01:30:21,750 --> 01:30:23,463
(SHRIEKING)

1044
01:30:24,453 --> 01:30:26,132
(SCREAMING)

1045
01:30:26,955 --> 01:30:28,873
(SCREAMS)

1046
01:30:29,023 --> 01:30:30,440
(YELLS)

1047
01:30:31,393 --> 01:30:32,794
Kim!

1048
01:30:32,795 --> 01:30:34,212
(SCREAMING)

1049
01:30:35,297 --> 01:30:36,715
No!

1050
01:30:39,501 --> 01:30:41,475
(SHRIEKS)

1051
01:30:42,971 --> 01:30:44,479
(SCREAMS)

1052
01:30:49,478 --> 01:30:52,022
(SOBBING)

1053
01:30:54,749 --> 01:30:56,167
Sally?

1054
01:30:58,253 --> 01:30:59,692
Sally?

1055
01:30:59,755 --> 01:31:02,270
Sally, are you okay?
Sally.

1056
01:31:05,728 --> 01:31:07,146
[KIM]: Alex?

1057
01:31:10,732 --> 01:31:12,867
(KIM SCREAMING)

1058
01:31:12,868 --> 01:31:14,286
Kim! (GASPING)

1059
01:31:17,673 --> 01:31:19,091
Kim!

1060
01:31:25,379 --> 01:31:26,955
Kim!

1061
01:31:31,387 --> 01:31:32,860
Dad?

1062
01:31:33,890 --> 01:31:35,306
Daddy?

1063
01:31:38,861 --> 01:31:39,961
(SOBBING)

1064
01:31:39,962 --> 01:31:41,379
Daddy.

1065
01:31:41,663 --> 01:31:43,172
Please!

1066
01:31:54,976 --> 01:31:56,894
(CRYING)

1067
01:33:32,006 --> 01:33:33,754
That's far enough, Sally.

1068
01:33:45,052 --> 01:33:46,868
I love you, Kim.

1069
01:34:49,118 --> 01:34:52,555
