1071
01:34:54,158 --> 01:34:57,574
[KIM WHISPERING]:
No, we will go deeper,

1072
01:34:58,459 --> 01:35:00,343
and we will wait.

1073
01:35:01,097 --> 01:35:03,997
They will forget,
and others will come.

1074
01:35:03,998 --> 01:35:05,167
