When will they come?

1075
01:35:05,468 --> 01:35:06,767
When will we get them?

1076
01:35:06,768 --> 01:35:09,379
[KIM]: Soon, soon.

1077
01:35:10,438 --> 01:35:14,108
- We have all the time in the world.
- Yes.

1078
01:35:14,109 --> 01:35:17,011
[KIM]:
All the time in the world.

1079
